data.eml:eml: Two new goby species of the genus Eviota from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan (Teleostei: Gobiidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Greenfield, David W., Suzuki, Toshiyuki (2011): Two new goby species of the genus Eviota from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan (Teleostei: Gobiidae). Zootaxa 2812: 63-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.277150
